flowchart TB
    U[User runs CLI] --> C[run command]
    C --> S[ralph.sh]
    S --> V[Validate PRD and tools]
    V --> E[Read next epic from PRD]
    E --> B{Epic ready}
    B -->|No| K[Skip epic]
    B -->|Yes| TL

    subgraph CS[Claude session: team agents for one epic]
        direction TB
        TL[Team lead]
        P[Planner creates plan]
        Q{Story already passed}
        BU[Builder implements]
        VA[Validator checks]
        R{Validation passed}
        W[Mark story passed in PRD]
        F[Record failure]
        M{More stories}
        RF[Write result file]

        TL --> P
        P --> Q
        Q -->|Yes| M
        Q -->|No| BU
        BU --> VA
        VA --> R
        R -->|Yes| W
        R -->|Retry left| BU
        R -->|No retry left| F
        W --> M
        F --> M
        M -->|Yes| Qmake
        M -->|No| RF
    end

    K --> ME{More epics}
    RF --> P2[Update epic status]
    P2 --> L[Append progress log]
    L --> ME
    ME -->|Yes| E
    ME -->|No| D[Finish run]